Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:26.79,box,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:24.95,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.79,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:29.02,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:31.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You said that a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:40.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.77,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.18,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,You were tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:47.56,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The city's different from \Nhow it was back then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.79,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.94,lake,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Lake Kiriya City
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.31,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:11.96,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}Saucer City
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.96,mail,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Furumiya      Shuichi\NKaori \NNonoka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.27,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:33.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I should have pulled out the batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.97,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is Dad's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.96,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.21,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.70,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.28,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep while I was unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.89,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long trip. I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't had breakfast, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I should have bought \Nsomething yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,About today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.43,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.33,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're stuck, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.84,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.15,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You grew another hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.09,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.07,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You know I'm the banner girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:41.77,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Banner girl doesn't mean you're \Nin charge of the banners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.64,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:47.86,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Switch over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.62,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.80,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,These saucer buns:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.91,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,how are they any different from \Nthe buns we were eating before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.43,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,How they look, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:15.64,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that thing's giving \Nyou a ton of trouble, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:23.65,shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shiihara Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.70,sora-main-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.31,sora-main-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It brought in a lot of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.16,sora-main-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun talking to all kinds of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:27.03,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So much for your summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.30,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been helping with the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:38.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that things have\Nchanged since then, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I'm almost done washing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's clean up together after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.12,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.77,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.86,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,they really want me to take over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.99,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I should be back by night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But what about cleaning and shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.15,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:29.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.95,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka! Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.33,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:19.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.63,sora-main,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,This'll keep me in the fight for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.20,sora-main,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.42,sora-main,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.75,sora-main,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.34,sora-main,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? You cheapo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.44,sora-main,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,That's such an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Your name's Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:19.95,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you lots, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why were you in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:36.38,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I was at that spot forever, \Nbut I got tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Where we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I get the sense that I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:57.40,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because we were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:58.95,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.60,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back right away, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.40,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.78,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:55.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Nonoka can't talk because she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.74,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there, I'll be back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.11,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.09,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bother coming back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:38.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.66,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.99,sora-flashback,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.74,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,See, it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:56.21,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, but I got nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.09,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.90,sora-flashback,Yuka,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.43,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Just once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.68,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.41,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get home before it gets deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.10,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.56,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.54,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty soon, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:27.24,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.15,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.25,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.62,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.12,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:24.96,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:28.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.36,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.27,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:49.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but never show up in front of me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.56,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.41,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.01,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad, running off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.51,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.48,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was being careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.52,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.00,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I did that by accident while \Nwe were packing in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.02,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I bought one on my way home from work
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.20,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,to fix it before you'd noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.88,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.64,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:25.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize lots to Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:36.30,boat,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Motor boats
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.06,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.71,lake2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Lake Kiriya Shore\N{\b0}Shiihara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.89,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:21.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's just that \NI'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,A small girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.67,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Is she lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a girl named Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She's dressed weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.00,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Is she from abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was hopeless to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:45.26,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Never show up in front of me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.25,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.46,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom is even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.95,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause Mom taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.78,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,She's even better than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.50,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:36.48,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your mom sing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:43.42,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Both me and Mom are leaving town today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.52,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:49.09,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.69,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'll bring Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.94,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell her about you. \NShe'd be glad to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.31,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.30,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.83,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.24,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.30,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.30,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.73,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.75,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And I haven't said bye to everyone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.55,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to catch the ferry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.16,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give Mom so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.96,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are we coming back here right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.57,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.26,sora-flashback,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,All three of us will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:10.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.03,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I believed you'd come back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.31,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.74,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.58,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's my turn \Nto fulfill my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:52.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's what I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:00.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,To grant your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.44,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial Method{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.10,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,"Their Promise."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:37.35,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:40.85,sora-next-ep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Their Promise
